The permission system is blocking writes to that directory. You need to approve the write permission in Claude Code settings. 

Run this in a separate terminal to check your permission mode:

```bash
cat ~/.claude/settings.json | grep -A5 permission
```

Or, if you're running in **auto-approve mode**, try running with:

```bash
claude --dangerously-skip-permissions
```

